comments: Great course; if you want to learn Chinese, it'll teach you Chinese. It's a lot of work, but you get what you put in.
Typical Chinese class with a great classroom atmosphere
It is a good continuation from Chinese L3 class.A textbook pretty much similar to the one used in L3 is usedand it doesn't get too difficult.
A natural progression from earlier steps, with a change in emphasis from the language to more cultural nuances in grammar and syntax
